{"tid":374091,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"日久見女神心","createTime":"2017-08-25T13:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T13:35:22.000Z","uid":140254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5590f689350d62ffe7592094b53daa4c9da9b17","tid":374091,"uid":140254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:23:50.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我有機會拎到女神電話同佢傾計啦<br />\n一開頭都好好嘅，日日都傾到佢瞓覺<br />\n有時仲一齊打機，得閒我都會做番兵仔會做嘅野，做下外賣仔<br />\n就咁過左三個幾月<br />\n有一日就如常咁傾計啦<br />\n但突然間佢已讀不回我又或者hea 覆我<br />\n好似想盡快終結對話咁<br />\n唉，咁我可以點🤷🏿&zwj;♂️<br />\n所以毒撚溝女神係唔會有好結果<br />\n電視成功嘅例子都係唔可信<br />\n美女與野獸都係厄你<br />\n因為男主角野變野獸嗰陣係靚仔，所以女主角用主角之眼睇得出係靚仔所以比佢溝<br />\n仲有個原因：因為佢係男主角所以溝到女主角"},{"pid":"c6a199e8dbb6267f12c62eab72e94644e7d37c9f","tid":374091,"uid":138223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"咁咪放棄lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74f6f86102450a30bbfb7bbde48c78660d841a2","tid":374091,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"我都係兩三個月左右比人開始已讀不回.HEA覆<br />\n之後我都無再搵佢了..."},{"pid":"706c4806c29c0b88d243598af1d82546cd652f69","tid":374091,"uid":52596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76e6af7560d7fb0dd6a8de102ff2f06fceddf8e","tid":374091,"uid":140254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係兩三個月左右比人開始已讀不回.HEA覆<br />\n之後我都無再搵佢了...</blockquote><br />\n兩三個月應該就係佢對你有新鮮感，之後冇曬"},{"pid":"dc96a5b7dd621a431d1d4a69a4be79c2e9ff77b4","tid":374091,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"ME TOO B